Package: jointcenteR
Title: Perform routine Joint Center calculations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Whitney", "Airgood-Obrycki", , "whitney_airgood-obrycki@harvard.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3644-1716"))
Description: Calculates weighted and unweighted tables with counts and shares or medians for large survey datasets.
    Inflates continuous variables to target year dollars using CPI-U All Items, and inflates rents to target year dollars
    using CPI-U Less Shelter. Can be used for tabulating datasets such as the American Community Survey or the American Housing Survey.
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    Hmisc,
    lubridate,
    tidyquant,
    tidyr
Suggests:
    testthat
